website_summaries.verdict: Become the skaters that you want with the high-top Osiris D3H. Among the Osiris D3H with a budget-friendly rate, this skate shoe offers performance and comfort that one needs to execute their tricks and flips. It has a richly padded upper and footbed, offering breathable wear and comfort.You can also level up your game with this high-top shoe built with a cupsole construction. It provides durability and performance. With the herringbone tread, the rubber outsole ensures a sure-footed grip.
pros: Many users have attested that the Osiris D3H is a comfortable shoe perfect for skateboarding and daily activities
Among the Osiris sneakers, this model is made of good material as per some of the customers
A lot of buyers are astonished by the skate shoe’s nice-looking and impressive design
The Osiris D3H provides better arch support than the Osiris NYC83, according to a skateboarder
Plenty of purchasers have perceived that it is a perfect skate shoe worthy of every penny
It is among the high-top sneakers from Osiris that are recommended by most of the reviewers
cons: The Osiris D3H has a narrow toe box compared to the Nike Dunk High, according to a few

customer_reviews.title: Exactly what i was looking for.
customer_reviews.text: Had a pair of D3 low tops way back in 02. Best shoes i have owned. When I found these I couldn't say no, I wear them daily. Love them, Thanks!
customer_reviews.author: Tamara

customer_reviews.title: Fit woman's 8
customer_reviews.text: I wear a women's size 8, the men's 6 for perfectly!! Was so happy these shoes worked out since it's getting harder and harder to find small sized Osiris'
customer_reviews.author: Thomas Donegan

customer_reviews.title: Sizes changed?
customer_reviews.text: All my husband wears is Osiris shoes. He loves them. This pair however was way too large? He always wears a size 10. These ones were swimming on him. We have to send back.
customer_reviews.author: Amy

customer_reviews.title: Tiny toe box
customer_reviews.text: Had to return because the toe box is essentially sewed shut... poor design. It’s like high heels in a flat shoe. Darn, they missed the mark.

customer_reviews.text: I had the blue version when these originally came out. Love these shoes, look just as awesome as they did back in the day.

customer_reviews.title: I'm pretty sure these will last him much longer
customer_reviews.text: These skate shoes ended up being way nicer looking than we thought. My son loves them. I've been buying skate shoes for my boys for many years and these are probably the strongest well made skate shoes i have ever bought. My kid blows out of his shoes every 3 or 4 months. I'm pretty sure these will last him much longer. I'm shocked i got these for such a good price . I've had pretty good luck when buying Osiris shoes though . I highly recommend these for kids t hat are really hard on shoes.
customer_reviews.author: Deanna

product_meta.title: Osiris Men's D3H Skate Shoe Black/camo, 7.5 M US
product_meta.description:
Description:
With a high-top silhouette and sporting flashy crimson hues throughout, the Osiris D3H Skate Shoes are built tough with a leather/synthetic canvas upper and TPU side wall lace closure details. A unique composition that boasts skate functionality with the aesthetic of high fashion streetwear.

Features:
- High-top design.
- Leather and synthetic canvas upper with double stitched toe and TPU side wall lace closure details.
- Oversized padded tongue with elastic straps for snug fit.
- Mesh lined interior.
- Padded high top collar.
- Cushioned EVA insole for comfort.
- Cupsole construction for durable performance.
- Osiris herringbone tread pattern on bottom for grip.
- Osiris logo detailing throughout.
